{"query":"SELECT Id, Name,
    CASE(Is_Customer__c, 
         true, 'Customer',
         false, 
            CASE(Has_Open_Opportunity__c,
                 true, 'Open Opp',
                 false, 
                    CASE(Has_Closed_Lost_Opportunity__c,
                         true, 'Closed Lost',
                         false, 'None')))
    END AS change_type
FROM Account
WHERE CreatedDate = LAST_N_MONTHS:12
    AND Is_Likely_Irrelevant__c = false"}
